    {
      "turn_id": 1,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "我们需要为PoTicTac这个教育类井字棋游戏绘制一个用户旅程图，重点展示首次玩家的完整体验路径。从发现游戏开始，经过引导、游戏对战、胜负结算，最后到持续参与。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "PoTicTac",
        "First-Time Player",
        "Discovery",
        "Onboarding",
        "Gameplay",
        "Victory/Defeat",
        "Engagement"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白了，这是一个复古风格的教育游戏。我想确认一下，旅程图需要包含哪些参与方？目前看来主要是Player，但AI和System也会在某些环节出现？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Player",
        "AI",
        "System"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "对，Player是核心，但AI在对战环节出现，System负责加载和结算。我们先从Discovery阶段开始：玩家找到游戏、加载网站，然后看到复古设计——这三步都是5分满意度。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Discovery",
        "Find the game",
        "Load website",
        "See retro design"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好的，Discovery部分已添加。接下来是Onboarding引导阶段，我记录了：输入玩家名称、选择单人模式、选择难度、点击开始游戏。其中输入名称这一步满意度是4分，其他都是5分。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Onboarding",
        "Enter player name",
        "Choose Single Player",
        "Select difficulty",
        "Click Start Game"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "Gameplay阶段最关键：玩家看到6x6棋盘、走第一步、等待AI回应、继续对战、最后看到制胜一击。等待AI那一步满意度稍低，给4分，因为可能会有轻微延迟。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Gameplay",
        "See 6x6 board",
        "Make first move",
        "Wait for AI",
        "Continue playing",
        "See winning move"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "6x6棋盘比传统3x3大很多，这是教育版的设计特色对吧？Victory/Defeat阶段我理解为：显示结果弹窗、查看统计更新、点击再玩一次。查看统计是4分，其他5分。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "6x6 board",
        "Victory/Defeat",
        "See result modal",
        "View stats update",
        "Click Play Again"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 7,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "没错，大棋盘是为了教学策略思维。最后一个Engagement阶段：查看排行榜、看到自己的排名、返回继续游戏。查看排行榜是4分，因为可能需要加载时间。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Engagement",
        "Check Leaderboard",
        "See ranking",
        "Return to play"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 8,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "完成！整个旅程图已覆盖五个阶段，从发现到持续参与。我注意到首次玩家的体验整体很流畅，主要摩擦点在数据加载相关的环节——输入名字、等待AI、查看排行榜和统计更新。",
